These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, filmmaking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, animation, romance
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, funk, metal
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching romance movies##2
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the fan of metal is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | traveling | drawing   | filmmaking   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | zombie | romance |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | pop    | funk      |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | roller      | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, apple, kiwi
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, trance, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, chinese, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, mouse
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the person eating apple is the nigerian##1
4. the person eating cranberry is the chinese##1
5. the owner of the fish is between the fan of trance and the person eating kiwi##2
6. the person eating kiwi is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | apple  | cranberry     | kiwi     |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | rock     | folk      |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | chinese | egyptian |
| Pet           | mouse | fish     | hamster       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, pineapple, cherry
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, videographer, lawyer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, action
3 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, frog
1. the chef is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the lawyer and the person watching action movies##2
3. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the lizard is the person eating pineapple##1
5. the owner of the mouse is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | strawberry  | cherry     | pineapple     |
| Job           | lawyer | chef  | videographer   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | animation    | action |
| Pet           | frog     | mouse | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, pumpkin, pepper
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, chef, bartender
3 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person eating pepper is between the chef and the owner of the frog##2
4. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | orange       | pepper  | pumpkin   |
| Job     | chef    | bartender  | freelancer |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | goldfish | frog        |
| Sport   | lacrosse | baseball     | golf      |

