.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, onion, grapes
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, card-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, pop, reggae
3 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, rabbit
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of reggae and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | grapes    | pear     | onion      |
| Hobby         | writing | magic-tricks | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | pop       | d&b       |
| Pet           | mouse     | turtle       | rabbit     |

