.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, apricot, kiwi
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, dancing, camping
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, salsa, gospel
3 different pets are kept: goat, pony, goldfish
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating kiwi is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the fan of salsa is between the person eating apricot and the owner of the pony##2
4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | apricot | pomegranate | kiwi    |
| Hobby         | dancing | camping      | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | house   | salsa     | gospel        |
| Pet           | goat      | goldfish       | pony      |

