.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, onion, pineapple
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, singing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, romance
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, tram
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating pineapple and the person driving the snowmobile##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person watching thriller movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | pineapple      | onion   | asparagus |
| Hobby         | puzzles | photography | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | romance | mystery   |
| Transport     | tram         | train  | snowmobile       |

