The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, camping, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, project-manager
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, reggae, ambient
1. the project-manager is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the lawyer is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta       | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate      |
| Hobby         | camping    | woodworking | gardening      |
| Job           | project-manager | lawyer     | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | ambient          | funk       |

