The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, architect
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, boat, skateboard
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the mechanic is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the architect##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fisherman##1
6. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | video-games       | fishing       | collecting    |
| Job         | architect | mechanic | fisherman |
| Sport       | badminton      | tennis         | basketball |
| Transport   | van        | skateboard            | boat  |

