.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, french, turkish
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the french is in the middle##1
4. the french is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | water     | sprite | fanta      |
| Hobby         | card-games  | puzzles       | baking |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | dubstep         | rock     |
| Nationality   | colombian | french    | turkish     |

