3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | dancing | fishing | skydiving |
| Pet         | rabbit   | guinea-pig       | turtle        |
| Sport       | handball | surfing   | water-polo         |
| Transport   | skateboard    | car     | subway         |

