3. the fan of punk is the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of d&b##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the cat##1
6. the british is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | punk | d&b  | country     |
| Nationality   | canadian    | dutch | british |
| Pet           | horse        | chinchilla   | cat  |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | bus   | skateboard |

