2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the musician##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the lizard##1
4. the freelancer is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
6. the electrician is between the musician and the fan of classical##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
