The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, chess, singing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, soul
3 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, lizard
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of gospel is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
4. the fan of electronic is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk     | lemonade        |
| Hobby         | chess   | singing | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | electronic        | gospel       | soul      |
| Pet           | lizard           | dog    | chinchilla       |

