.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, apricot, orange
3 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, rowing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, ship
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the owner of the fish is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating orange##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the ship and the person who's sport is rowing##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | apricot      | peas | orange |
| Pet         | fish     | hedgehog    | lizard        |
| Sport       | rowing | water-polo   | volleyball   |
| Transport   | skateboard          | quad-bike     | ship       |

 